s://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003258_7954955894601079_689785468504338862_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TsKWAc6i2gAQ7kNvgF7XJk2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBD8ewBBJNJVnLK4x4yI68Qeh6aXpOcjA-IDy3Z26l_yg&oe=671CD5A6"}, "display_name": "Merlin's Chess Beta", "keywords": [], "long_description": "\ud83d\udca1 \"If you\u2019ve ever dreamed of experiencing the magic of Wizard\u2019s Chess in a fully immersive VR environment, Merlin's Chess is your gateway to that world, and even more.\"\n\n\ud83d\udca1 \"Perfect for chess enthusiasts and beginners alike.\"\n\n**Step into the world of Merlin's Chess, where strategy meets magic!**\n\nMerlin's Chess is a fantasy-themed VR chess game brings a completely new gameplay experience to the greatest strategy game ever. Explore an immersive and enchanting way to play chess.\n\n# Rich Set of Features\n\n- **\ud83d\udca5 Animated Chess Pieces:** Experience massive, animated chess pieces coming to life and clashing each other with captivating visual and sound effects.\n- **\ud83c\udf99\ufe0f Voice Commands:** Command your pieces with your voice. Many other in-game voice commands are also supported.\n- **\ud83c\udf0d Matchmaking:** Find worthy opponents from around the world who match your skill level.\n- **\ud83e\udd16 Play vs. AI:** Challenge AI NPCs with a wide range of difficulty levels.\n- **\ud83c\udfae Game Modes:** Multiple game modes to serve every need. **Casual Mode** for a calm experience, **Ranked Mode** if feeling competitive, and upcoming **Puzzle Mode**!\n- **\ud83c\udf7f Spectator Mode:** Join ongoing games as spectator, hangout with other players, and feel the competition.\n- **\ud83c\udfc6 Rating System**: Glicko-2 based pro-grade rating system for competitive matches. \n- **\ud83c\udff0 Fancy Content**: Seasonal Themes, New Match Environments, New Piece Sets, New Command Stations. Always fresh and inspiring!\n - **\ud83d\udc69\ud83c\udffd\u200d\ud83e\udd1d\u200d\ud83d\udc68\ud83c\udffb Social by Default:** Customizable Avatars, Voice Chat, and Friendship System.", "short_description": "\ud83d\udca1 \"If you\u2019ve ever dreamed of experiencing the magic of Wizard\u2019s Chess in a fully immersive VR environment, Merlin's Chess is your gateway to that world, and even more.\"\n\nMerlin's Chess offers an immersive and enchanting way to play chess with a rich feature set including a variety of game modes, animated chess pieces, multiplayer gameplay, voice commands, AI opponents, piece sets, match environments, spectator mode, and additional DLC content support for exciting new themes."}]}, "developer_name": "Teleporter Realities", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://merlinschess.gg/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://merlinschess.gg/terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "Teleporter Realities", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://merlinschess.gg/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1573854509480616"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "275629210202852"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE", "STANDING", "SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "8123230434430275"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001708_1712686689540605_7162334905017180889_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Hjm_xuiD7K8Q7kNvgFy1-rG&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_A